window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>True love can blossom anywhere, in a government set-up, too, and can be as permanent as the job itself. </p><p>Shalini, a government employee, strongly feels that there is no point in getting married and joining the brigade of abused wives. Till she is swept off her feet by Kartik, a dynamic colleague from Bihar. </p><p>Just when her faith in the system of love and marriage is rekindled and at its peak, Kartik goes missing. Her search for him reveals some dark secrets about Zabaria Shaadi, still existing in Bihar, where eligible boys are abducted or forced for marriage. </p><p>A love story at its core, <i>Love Forever @Rajpath</i> highlights the predicaments of a girl on the verge of losing her most precious relationship. It also reflects the inner turmoil of a young boy sandwiched between age-old traditions and his own liberated opinions. </p><p>Will Shalini be able to save her relationship? Will Kartik acknowledge her efforts, or will he abandon her for the sake of his family? </p>"; 
